reviewText: THE VOICE THAT THRILLED MILLIONS. GREAT TO SEE AND HEAR.
This was a gift, for a real Corelli fan. She loved it.

lovely video with a nice documentery  about 21minutes on mr corelli . then  we have songs and arias from different eras in the life of franco corelli its a great dvd for all lovers of the great  franco corelli
If you love Corelli at his prime, you will enjoy this.
